OL,3,CMan dressed as a clown steals
OL,4,Cvaluables from pensioner's house
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Fafter a man dressed as a clown talked
OL,8,Fhis way into a pensioner's house and
OL,9,Fstole valuable items.
OL,11,FIt happened on Friday 31 October at a
OL,12,Fhouse on Birch Road in Rochdale.
OL,14,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) say
OL,15,Faround 7.10pm, a woman answered the
OL,16,Fdoor to a man, who is believed to have
OL,17,Fbeen dressed in a clown outfit.
OL,19,FHe asked for a drink and then followed
OL,20,Fthe woman into her home and stole
OL,21,Fseveral items before running away.
