OL,3,CMan dressed as a clown steals
OL,4,Cvaluables from pensioner's house
OL,6,FHe took a red purse with the woman's
OL,7,Fmother's wedding ring, which is of
OL,8,Fextremely sentimental value.
OL,10,FHe may have discarded this once he
OL,11,Fleft the victim's address.
OL,13,FThe 75-year-old woman was unhurt but
OL,14,Fhas been left shocked and upset by the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FOfficers have now released an image of
OL,18,Fa man they would like to speak to, as
OL,19,Fit is believed he could help with
OL,20,Ftheir enquiries.
