OL,3,CMan dressed as a clown steals
OL,4,Cvaluables from pensioner's house
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Ruth Thompson, from
OL,7,FGMP's Rochdale district, said: "This
OL,8,Fwas a shocking incident, which has
OL,9,Fleft a woman feeling unsafe in her own
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,F"She has spent many years helping the
OL,13,Fhomeless and working for local
OL,14,Fcharities, so it is particularly grim
OL,15,Fthat someone would exploit her
OL,16,Fgoodwill.
OL,18,F"While I appreciate the image quality
OL,19,Fisn't the greatest, I hope that
OL,20,Fsomeone may recognise the costume and
OL,21,Fit jogs their memory.
